I believe I've run into a bug in the configuration of related resource links. I think the issue starts here:

[rest_framework_json_api/relations.py#L101][1]

The `related_kwargs` dict is not actually configurable. The `related_link_lookup_field` is only used to access `kwargs`, which, because `get_links` [is not called with any kwargs][2], has a kwarg `lookup_field` and is defaulted to "pk". It is rarely, if ever, that the child's lookup field is the parent's primary key, therein lies the problem. Here is an example of the **incorrect** output:

```json
{
  "data": {
    "id": 241,
    "relationships": {
      "previous-shipment": {
        "data": {
          "type": "shipment",
          "id": "1439417"
        },
        "links": {
          "self": "http://localhost:8000/api/account/241/relationships/previous_shipment",
          "related": "http://localhost:8000/api/shipment/241/"
        }
      }
    },
    "type": "account"
  }
}
```

You'll notice that the related link _should_ be http://localhost:8000/api/shipment/1439417


**Possible solution**

I'll happily make a PR for this, but it's confusing enough that I want to make sure I'm on the right track.

My guess is that the `related_kwargs` is just getting set wrong. The assignment seems to be a reflection of the assignment on [L95][3]. If that is the case, I think the code is just a bit off (this was tested and works):

```py
related_kwargs = {self.related_link_url_kwarg: getattr(obj, self.related_link_lookup_field) if obj else kwargs[self.related_link_lookup_field]}
```


[1]: https://github.com/django-json-api/django-rest-framework-json-api/blob/79b7c79f0c19fdda77dfc62e2ad58cedaad73033/rest_framework_json_api/relations.py#L101
[2]: https://github.com/django-json-api/django-rest-framework-json-api/blob/79b7c79f0c19fdda77dfc62e2ad58cedaad73033/rest_framework_json_api/renderers.py#L160
[3]: https://github.com/django-json-api/django-rest-framework-json-api/blob/79b7c79f0c19fdda77dfc62e2ad58cedaad73033/rest_framework_json_api/relations.py#L95

